{"tid":553354,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約警方開始用 iPhone 7 取代 Windows Phone","createTime":"2018-02-07T11:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T02:11:45.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3d37d7f88bb9f10cf7ad86ff543b5db4755181af","tid":553354,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07101727/10485276334_846dd6f495_o1-e1517969867227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F07101727%2F10485276334_846dd6f495_o1-e1517969867227.jpg&h=5a5df13e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n2017 年美國紐約警方公布將由 Windows Phone 全面轉用 iPhone，現在已落實。36,000 部警方專用 Windows Phone 會在兩年內轉換，大部分是前線人員用的手機。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07101050/iphones5n-3-web-2-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F07101050%2Fiphones5n-3-web-2-768x432.jpg&h=6bbcd16e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據《紐約每日新聞》報導，紐約警方已開始每日發放 600 部 iPhone 給警務人員，有 iPhone 7 與 iPhone 7 Plus。現在曼哈頓區的警察已換機，之後會陸續發放布魯克林區與皇后區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/02/07/nypd-begins-deploying-iphone-7-7-plus-to-officers-as-it-officially-moves-on-from-windows-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2Fnypd-begins-deploying-iphone-7-7-plus-to-officers-as-it-officially-moves-on-from-windows-phone%2F&d=0NtIp6AWbsTciRjD%2FUosWP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0f5ad7d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/02/07/nypd-begins-deploying-iphone-7-7-plus-to-officers-as-it-officially-moves-on-from-windows-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"98e8ebc8ac9269e30b8fe0a066c2860a5a6a427a","tid":553354,"uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"換機後警察大多表示滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有警察指「是巡邏警察最適用的工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，有警察指智慧手機接收訊息比無線電通訊還快：「911 求助熱線收到的個案會很快在手機顯示，地點也很清楚，有時收到無線電通知時，我們已在現場」。根據統計，警方到達現場的時間比以往快 14%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"e99db373be6f444e2f5186e9f10aec250323e413","tid":553354,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"在此之前，有警察曾不滿 Windows Phone 使用時不方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。轉換 iPhone 之前，紐約警察一般都用 Lumia 640 XL 及 Lumia 830，這些手機也只用了約兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/07101049/2017-08-28-image-31-768x512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F07101049%2F2017-08-28-image-31-768x512.jpg&h=621ab22c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"543e65bd25acb091f93e37566eb3b4ccd0f6e2c5","tid":553354,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832e12d0b0260b6fd27a4fa144ace9a6a11678a3","tid":553354,"uid":8921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"居然用windows phone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bac52be8cfd02562a9ae62eab32bfb0b5a3862","tid":553354,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"呢啲係咪叫貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdafc76d73759c7ec68dbc244f73418a1987ee3f","tid":553354,"uid":623,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"iPhone = Windows Phone &gt; Android Phon